<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī</hi> kOpparakeca
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ri pa<hi rend="grantha">nma</hi>kku yāṇṭu 4 Āvatu tirumaṇa
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ñcēri paramasvāmikku tañcāvūr ma
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṭaippaḷḷip peṇṭāṭṭi palatēva
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ḷaṅkiṭacāṉai vaitta no
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ntāviḷakku 1 Itu Erikka ni
<lb n="7" break="no"/>lai viḷakku 1 cāvāmūvāppērā
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṭu toṇṇūṟṟāṟu Ivai ve
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ṭṭiṉa kallu cantirāttaval
<lb n="10"/>paṉ mā<hi rend="grantha">hēśvara</hi>r Ira<hi rend="grantha">kṣai</hi>
</p>

